data.description: Introducing a stunning 5 bedroom, 4 bath home that embodies luxury living. This magnificent residence features an exquisite master suite w/spacious walk in closet & beautifully appointed spa-like en suite bathroom. The gourmet kitchen is equipped w/all the best amenities, it is a culinary enthusiast's dream. The adjacent breakfast room offers a cozy & inviting space for casual dining.  With a separate dining area, entertaining guests is effortless & elegant.  To top it off this home boasts a 2-car garage, ensuring ample parking & storage.  Experience the epitome of comfort and sophistication with this picture perfect home!!
